text: te puokke ban yk preah neanea mk korp sakkar phe sa ng pi trong del puokvea min ach bangkeut avei ban tealtesaoh te puokvea vinh te del trauv ke( mnoussa lok) bangkeut noh . haey preah teangnoh kmean lotthopheap knong kar karpar krohthnak ning phdal phalobrayoch champohkhluon eng laey . haey puokke kmean lotthopheap thveu aoy slab ning thveu aoy rsa laey haeyka kmean lotthopheap theu v aoy rsa laengvinh der( now thngai barlok)
